## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v16 or higher)
- npm or yarn

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/EthanK511/Out-There-Dashboard.git
   cd Out-There-Dashboard
   ```

2. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. **Configure API keys**
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   ```
   
