## ğŸ¯ Aviation Widget Heuristic

The Aviation widget uses a scoring algorithm to select the most "viewable" flight:

**Scoring Criteria**:
- **Altitude** (50 pts): Flights between 5,000-12,000m (optimal viewing altitude)
- **Speed** (30 pts): Flights faster than 200 km/h (commercial jets)
- **Route Info** (20 pts): Complete departure and arrival data
- **Airline Info** (10 pts): Has airline name

The flight with the highest score is displayed with real-time position, altitude, and speed data.

